<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-08 13:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9344 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBO-SCOUT-TEXT-REVIEW     05-08 0881
