<SLUG> BC-EVEREST-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EVEREST ACCOUTERMENT, THEN AND NOW 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
