5-08 -- Yossi Beilin, a soft-spoken, bespectacled academic who is
serving as the right wing's voodoo doll in the current election
campaign in Israel. Beilin, has established working relations with
the Palestinians. While he is invisible on the public stage of his
own Labor Party, Beilin, a leftist, is prominently featured as
archenemy by the conservative Likud Party and its supporters. (Rina
Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
